					<description><![CDATA[<p>This pandemic time could prove to be a blessing in disguise for the hotel and hospitality industry to shift their focus on travel technology solutions.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/top-custom-software-solutions-for-the-travel-hospitality-industry">Top Custom Software Solutions For The Travel &#038; Hospitality Industry</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog">Aryavrat</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The travel and hospitality industry has drastically changed over the last decade, from management and marketing activities to consumer behavior everything has seen a complete Turnaround.</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">A recent survey carried out by </span><a href="https://www.aryausa.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Travel Technology Solution USA </a><span style="font-weight: 400;">made some surprising revelations about challenges faced by the travel and hospitality industry.</span></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" class="alignright wp-image-2084" src="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Travel1.jpeg" alt="Travel" width="284" height="284" srcset="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Travel1.jpeg 1500w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Travel1-300x300.jpeg 300w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Travel1-1024x1024.jpeg 1024w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Travel1-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Travel1-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Travel1-200x200.jpeg 200w" sizes="(max-width: 284px) 100vw, 284px" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Around 40 percent of respondents identified that gaps in technical skills as a key challenge within the industry that needs to be addressed.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Otherwise, It is just like giving a walk over to the Millions of companies out there that are making an all-out effort to increase their customer base and If you are still longing for the days when a customer </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">will walk into your hotel and says – “Do you have a room available?” are long go</span>ne. by adopting new innovative technological solutions at the time of this pandemic are need of the hour than ever before.</p>
<p>This pandemic time could prove to be a blessing in disguise for the hotel and hospitality industry to shift their focus on travel technology solutions to update their businesses to adapt to the new normal to sustain in this industry.</p>
<h3>Online Check-in-</h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">It simplifies the guest arrival process and increases productivity by saving unnecessary time spent on manual check-in.</span></p>
<h3>Multi-currency and Language-</h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To attract foreign clients one has to have a website or booking platforms that support multiple currencies and languages.</span></p>
<h3>Advanced user search-</h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">It allows the client to search and get the desired results.</span></p>
<h3>Secure payment gateway-</h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">For making online booking payments it&#8217;s a must ask for a booking Platform.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Travel technology Solution specifically focuses on <a href="https://infobloger.medium.com/how-does-travel-software-simplify-the-travel-business-57822832a0b1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Developing Travel Software</a> such as tour operator software, travel agency software, various travel booking platforms, website development, integration of XML/ API/GDS to ease out the travel business intricacies and increase the revenue by multifold.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">A committed and experienced </span>Travel Software &amp; <a href="https://www.aryausa.com/mobile-app-development" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mobile App Development Services in USA</a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> could bring a paradigm shift in any travel business either you work at a small scale or a gigantic firm, by using innovative travel technology solutions you can automate business procedures, robust travel booking engine for flights, for applying visas, packages &amp; car rentals through a score of sales channels like B2C &amp; B2B significantly bring down the business expenses and improves customer experience, etc.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Now when we talk about the core features of a tour operator software they may not come into notice more often but they significantly impact from behind the scenes. Customer Repository and CRM- customer Repositories and Inbuilt CRM complement each other really well, they play a crucial role in tour operator software to track day-to-day activities and to store client&#8217;s info.</span></p>
<h2><b>Accounts Management</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Accounts &amp; finance management is an integral part of any business. Tour operator software ought to have an easy and expeditious accounting feature that can automate travel business processes such as invoice creation, Tax generation, Automatic entries in multiple accounting fields, Auto display of tax%, accounting history storage.</span></p>
<h2>Application Programmable Interface</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">It is widely known as API, it is considered as one of the most essential components of a tour operator software, one can take advantage of it by using numerous forms such as hotel APIs, holiday APIs, flight APIs, car APIs, etc. It can be a major time-saving parameter for tour operators, as they can combine many platforms like flight booking, hotel booking, etc, and get a complete hold of their business in order to provide quick and excellent services to their customers, tour operator software with a B2C web portal gives an additional advantage.</span></p>
<h2>Secure Payment Gateways</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Secure payment gateways are really important for making online transactions there are multiple payment gateway options are available such as PayPal, Paytm WePay, 2Checkout, and several others that guarantee flawless &amp; secure payment processes for both clients and hotelier or tour operators.</span></p>
<h2>Multi-currency &amp; Multilingual</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Tour operators have to go across the board to attract a larger customer base across the globe, multiple currencies and language supportability is required in a good tour operator software or portal, having only indigenous language support could limit the reach and become a hurdle to growth in terms of sales.</span></p>
<p><a href="https://www.aryausa.com/get-in-touch" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-2083" src="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Travel3.jpeg" alt="Our Solutions For Travel &amp; Hospitality " width="602" height="83" srcset="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Travel3.jpeg 725w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Travel3-300x41.jpeg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 602px) 100vw, 602px" /></a></p>
<h2>In-Depth Reporting</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In-depth research and analysis could help you to a great extent to make correct decisions for your travel business.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Auto-generation of valuable reports has now become a really important feature for tour operator software, auto-generation of all reports such as accounting reports, tour report business reports, etc. it gives you a clear insight of your business.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If we dig deeper this list could go on and on but the features that we have mentioned above are the core ones or the heart of any tour operator software, this could help you to make a to-do list for your </span><a href="https://www.aryausa.com/success-stories">Travel Technology Company USA</a><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span></p>
