					<description><![CDATA[<p>As says health is your wealth. So, are you interested in an app development for healthcare? Or do you want to resolve issues in the industry?</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/healthcare-app-development-essential-things-you-need-to-know">Healthcare App Development: Essential Things You Need To Know</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog">Aryavrat</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As says health is your wealth. So, are you interested in developing an application for healthcare? Or do you want to resolve some issues in the healthcare industry?</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Then you are thinking right; this is the best time for healthcare app development. The Covid-19 outbreak has made us realize that the global healthcare system needs to make some important adjustments to adapt to some new realities. It is important to monitor health conditions and visit doctors timely due to this situation it is hard to visit the doctor and have a checkup. Mobile apps help people to cope up with this.  According to Statista research, the digital health market is expected to cost $206 billion by 2020.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Mobile health applications allow patients to connect with healthcare providers and staff more quickly. Apps designed for a mobile phone or tablet also allow the user to access information when and where they need it, reduce time wastage searching for data, and boosting engagement rate.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Some mHealth apps stats</span></h2>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">54% of patients have shown interest in the change from regular office appointments towards mobile interaction.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">⅓ of people have used apps so, they can communicate with their doctors in real-time.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">62% of people are not comfortable sharing their personal information with healthcare providers because of information misplacing.</span></li>
</ul>
<h2><strong>Steps of Healthcare Mobile App Development Services</strong></h2>
<h3><strong>Choose the best technological partner among healthcare Software Development Companies</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">When selecting the Best Healthcare <a href="https://www.aryausa.com/mobile-app-development" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mobile App Development Services in USA</a>, consider previous products, client reviews, and company tech expertise. So, you can select the best one for your app development.</span></p>
<h3><strong>Create a rough estimation of medical app development</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Decide the features and functionalities required on your app based on that create a rough estimation cost of developing a <a href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/why-react-native-trending-in-2020" target="_blank" rel="noopener">healthcare app development project</a>.</span></p>
<h3><strong>Start the development with the inception phase</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Clarify more details about your app by creating user stories, mockups, and wireframes.</span></p>
<h3><strong>Start developing the Healthcare App</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">After the inception phase starts developing and designing your healthcare app. </span></p>
<h2><strong>Features of Healthcare App Development</strong></h2>
<p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1872 size-full" src="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/28896-1-1024x512-1.jpg" alt="Healthcare App Development" width="1024" height="512" srcset="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/28896-1-1024x512-1.jpg 1024w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/28896-1-1024x512-1-300x150.jpg 300w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/28896-1-1024x512-1-768x384.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The Healthcare App Development process consists of UI/UX design creation, app development, back-end development, quality assurance, and maintenance. Here is the list of common features that can be included in the application.</span></p>
<h3><strong>Tracking</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This helps to monitor the patient&#8217;s blood pressure, heart rate, calorie consumption, and glucose level.</span></p>
<h3><strong>Scheduling</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This helps to book an appointment with a healthcare specialist easily. So, patients don&#8217;t have to stand in a queue. </span></p>
<h3><strong>Payment</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Payment features help the user to pay for healthcare services or insurance. </span></p>
<h3><strong>Social Integration</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This feature helps the user to share their personal information with third-party services.</span></p>
<h3><strong>Real-time chat</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This function gives the ability for patients to chat with the doctor and make trustworthy relationships between users and healthcare providers.</span></p>
<h3><strong>Feedback</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This feature gives the ability for patients to share their experience with a doctor and help other patients make the decision. </span></p>
<h3><strong>Notifications </strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This feature gives notifications about appointments with doctors, test results. </span></p>
<h3><strong>Data Security</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In this feature data shared by users is secured properly. So, no one can access that information. </span></p>
<h3><strong>Online Reports</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">All the test reports are piled up in one place so one can easily check their reports.</span></p>
<h2><strong>Type of Healthcare Apps</strong></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">All healthcare apps can be divided into two categories such as professional health care app and healthcare apps for patients.</span></p>
<h3><strong>Professional Healthcare App</strong></h3>
<h4><strong>Healthcare reference and database apps</strong></h4>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">These apps are used to keep all information regarding diseases, drugs, and prescriptions in one place.</span></p>
<h4><strong>Networking apps</strong></h4>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">These are social networking apps where all healthcare providers can contact, interact, exchange knowledge, and grow their professional community.</span></p>
<h4><strong>Patient health tracking apps</strong></h4>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This helps the doctor monitor the health of their patient throughout the treatment process. All test result reports and other documents are listed here.</span></p>
<h4><strong>Risk assessment apps</strong></h4>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This allows patient health condition monitoring in real-time, track heart rate, and identify patients at risk.</span></p>
<h4><strong>Barcode scanning apps</strong></h4>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">These apps allow scanning a patient’s electronic health record, medication barcodes using a built-in camera in their mobile devices.</span></p>
<h4><strong>Medication apps</strong></h4>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">These apps are used by physicians to calculate the patient doses of medicine based on the patient’s age, weight, and other personal info.</span></p>
<h3><strong>Healthcare Apps for Patients</strong></h3>
<p><b>Telemedicine apps</b></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Through these apps, patients can receive treatment and consultation from medical specialists without leaving their office or home.    </span></p>
<p><b>Fitness apps</b></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">These apps users keep fit by tracking their daily activity, weight, the number of calories burned, list of workout programs and can integrate with wearable devices. </span></p>
<p><b>Diet apps</b></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">These apps include a large library with food and nutrition, a calorie counter, a diary and meals, and a progress chart. </span></p>
<h2><strong>Benefits of Healthcare app</strong></h2>
<p><img loading="lazy" class="alignright wp-image-1687" src="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Healthcare_app_dev.png" alt="Online Doctor" width="302" height="302" srcset="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Healthcare_app_dev.png 500w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Healthcare_app_dev-300x300.png 300w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Healthcare_app_dev-150x150.png 150w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Healthcare_app_dev-200x200.png 200w" sizes="(max-width: 302px) 100vw, 302px" /></p>
<h3><strong>Improve Efficiency</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Productivity will be increased since the workflow is improved as services will be digitalized and some routine processes will be automated. This will help the doctor by replacing a pile of the document. </span></p>
<h3><strong>Numerous Feature</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">According to the app type, patients can check lab results, consult with doctors through chat, monitor their nutrition, track medication, and so on. Healthcare apps include many functionalities and developers can integrate everything you need.</span></p>
<h3><strong>No Distance Worry</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">How far a patient or physician is they can easily communicate with each other. Remote medical care will also be available. </span></p>
<h3><strong>Cost Reduction</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As patients can chat with doctors without visiting them, it reduces expenses and overall costing. Healthcare apps don’t need too much administrative work.</span></p>
<h3><strong>Anytime Access</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Patients can consult with a doctor anytime they need it without thinking about day or night. Patients can find answers to all their questions using the app. </span></p>
<h3><strong>Time-Saving</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Doctors can communicate with patients directly through the app furthermore this saves the time of doctors and patients. Both can find the required information <a href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/what-is-software-development-and-maintenance" target="_blank" rel="noopener">they need in the software</a>.</span></p>
<p>Mobile App Development<span style="font-weight: 400;"> empowers medical app developers to rapidly take into account healing crises and also enhance patient administration. From recommending solutions and viewing reports to following and checking suggestions, these applications assist experts to analyze, treat, and screen a number of diseases. we are one of the trusted Healthcare Mobile App development Companies that provide <a href="https://www.aryausa.com/get-in-touch" target="_blank" rel="noopener">m-health app solutions</a></span></p>
