					<comments>https://www.aryausa.com/blog/how-artificial-intelligence-is-changing-digital-marketing-industry#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 04 Sep 2020 12:49:41 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Digital Marketing]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Technology]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[AI and IoT solutions]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Artificial Intelligence Development Company]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Artificial Intelligence Development Company USA]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Artificial Intelligence Services]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Digital Marketing Service Provider Company]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Digital Marketing Services USA]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Digital Marketing Strtegies]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Search Engine Optimization Services USA]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[SEO Services Provider]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.aryausa.com/blog/?p=1634</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>Exciting technology needs to include the emergence of Artificial Intelligence, has already started making its mark in digital marketing.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/how-artificial-intelligence-is-changing-digital-marketing-industry">How Artificial Intelligence is Changing Digital Marketing Industry?</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog">Aryavrat</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The world of digital marketing is constantly changing. Everyday day new and exciting innovation is coming that helps the marketers take the digital marketing world to the next level. The most beneficial and exciting technology needs to include the emergence of Artificial Intelligence. Artificial Intelligence has already started making its mark in digital marketing and also the advancement in AI mainly focuses on the development of intelligent tools and changing the digital marketing world.</span> <span style="font-weight: 400;">In this article, we are going to discuss the use of AI in digital marketing. Digital marketing includes various fields such as </span><a href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/search-engine-optimization-seo-the-heart-of-your-online-success" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Search Engine Optimization</a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, Social Media Optimization, Pay Per Click, etc. Organizations use digital channels such as social media, emails, search engines to attach with the end-users.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">As we are looking forward to 2021, here is the list of some of the biggest AI-related digital marketing trends:</span></h2>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">AI has included email marketing, many organizations started using chatbots for user interaction.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Businesses are enhancing their SEO and content marketing strategies for voice search.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Big data is used in better personalization of marketing messages.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Augmented Reality and Virtual Reality used by many retail brands with great effects especially in apps. </span></li>
</ul>
<p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1880" src="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1913-1-1024x552-1.png" alt="Marketing Automation" width="663" height="358" srcset="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1913-1-1024x552-1.png 1024w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1913-1-1024x552-1-300x162.png 300w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1913-1-1024x552-1-768x414.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 663px) 100vw, 663px" /></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Artificial Intelligence impact on different Digital Marketing Strategies</span></h2>
<p><b>Artificial Intelligence</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> has revolutionized the digital marketing world. In the last few years, AI has innovated such powerful tools that not only help marketers in promoting their products and services in a better manner but also minimize the time and effort required to reach marketing goals.</span> <span style="font-weight: 400;">The main objective of </span><a href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/artificial-intelligence-and-its-challenges-with-solution" target="_blank" rel="noopener">why AI is so beneficial</a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> when it comes to marketing is that it simplifies the various operational processes and also adds a human element to the process which works as a key element for excellent marketing. </span> <span style="font-weight: 400;"> </span></p>
<h2><strong>Artificial Intelligence in Search Engine Optimization</strong></h2>
<h3><strong>Optimize Keywords</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">For better SEO it is important to gather suitable keywords for your business. This keyword planning can be done using various tools for keyword planning and keyword selection. Businesses can also analyze the keywords used by their competitors. The tools such as MOZ, Keyword Planner, etc used for keyword planning use artificial intelligence to analyze the keyword. While searching competitors&#8217; keywords AI scans the website and understands what your competitor is targeting more. </span></p>
<h3><strong>Predictive Analyzes </strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">There are many tools developed by Google that help to analyze previous data. But the predictive analysis helps to analyze future events. The analysis helps to identify future search trends that help in overall sales. The predictive analysis uses artificial intelligence to provide future insights. </span></p>
<h3><strong>Analyze the Customer Data</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">There is a lot of data generated every day. There are many tools available in the market that collect the customer data and analyze it to offer details to help the customer complete the purchase. In businesses, you should be able to predict the needs of the customer before they themself realize. AI conducts the analysis based on customer previous browsing and past purchase.</span></p>
<h3><strong>Chatbots</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">A chatbot adopted and integrated by many businesses on their websites and social media accounts to attract n number of users. Chatbot</span> <span style="font-weight: 400;">not only interacts with customers to solve their queries but also offers to buy suggestions to customers. The best part is a single bot can handle thousands of queries in a day. </span></p>
<h2><strong>Artificial Intelligence in Social Media Marketing</strong></h2>
<h3><strong>Content Optimization</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Social media not only include long texts but should also include images and videos. </span><a href="https://www.aryausa.com/Iot-solution" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Artificial Intelligence</a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> helps marketers to decide the marketing strategy.</span></p>
<h3><strong>Personal Buying Information</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Many users purchase products off the internet. Companies should have a smart way to sell their product. Artificial Intelligence learns user searching habits on social media.</span></p>
<h3><strong>Competitor Analysis</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Tracing and analyzing competitors is an effective strategy in which AI helps a lot. With the help of AI, you can run all equivalent analyses that you can run on your pages on competitors. This helps to see what’s operating and integrating and sum in their own strategy.</span></p>
<h3><strong>Customer Service</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Some customers make queries on social media and humans cannot provide support to all queries 24*7. The use of AI in customer support helps businesses to generate leads and boost conversion rates through social media marketing.</span> <span style="font-weight: 400;">Facebook highly invested in Artificial Intelligence so its face recognition saves a great deal of time for the user by tagging the individual on the picture. The App itself recognizes the individual in the picture by its biometric authentication technology. </span></p>
<p><a href="https://www.aryausa.com/get-in-touch" target="_blank" rel="https://www.aryausa.com/get-in-touch noopener noreferrer"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1882 size-full" src="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/request_a_quote_1.jpg" alt="Request A Quote " width="750" height="170" srcset="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/request_a_quote_1.jpg 750w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/request_a_quote_1-300x68.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" /></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Conclusion</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">AI in <a href="https://www.aryausa.com/digital-marketing-solutions" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Digital Marketing Services</a> makes things and processes easy. Whether you are a business owner or marketer it is important to stay updated with the ever-evolving trends in the world of digital marketing. Involving AI in digital marketing not only helps to market your product and services in a better way but also helps you gain a competitive edge in the market. </span><a href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/how-to-get-rid-of-issues-while-outsourcing-the-development-team" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Whether you are outsourcing this</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> or building them in-house you have to ultimately need them in order to compete in this changing world.</span></p>
