		<title>How Much Does a WordPress Website Development Cost?</title>
		<link>https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wordpress-website-development-cost</link>
					<comments>https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wordpress-website-development-cost#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 26 Aug 2020 13:34:53 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Technology]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Web Development]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Web development Company]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Web development Company USA]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Web Development Services]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[WordPress Web Development]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[WordPress Web Development Company]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[WordPress Web Development Company USA]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[WordPress Web Development Services]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[WordPress Web Development Services USA]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[WordPress Web Development USA]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.aryausa.com/blog/?p=1589</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>WordPress is free but one has to spend money on facts that will estimate the cost of WordPress web development such as hosting fees, domain costs.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wordpress-website-development-cost">How Much Does a WordPress Website Development Cost?</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog">Aryavrat</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">WordPress was started in 2003 by Matt Mullenweg and Mike Little. From there onward WordPress has come a long way and become one of the powerful software in the web development industry. WordPress has started as a simple blogging platform. But in recent years it has split into a full-blown Content Management System (CMS). </span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Here is the list of things to keep in mind before deciding the cost of WordPress website development</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">There are a number of factors that can affect the costing of <a href="https://www.aryausa.com/custom-software-development" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Web Development Services</a></span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Offered Services</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" class="alignright wp-image-1907" src="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wordpress_logo_318_9_W5tLm.jpg" alt="wordpress-logo" width="278" height="273" srcset="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wordpress_logo_318_9_W5tLm.jpg 626w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wordpress_logo_318_9_W5tLm-300x295.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 278px) 100vw, 278px" />WordPress services are of numerous types such as website development, WordPress customization, theme development, plugin development, WordPress integration, WordPress mobile website, WordPress maintenance, eCommerce development, etc. </span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Website Type</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The purpose and idea behind the development of the website can be a major factor in determining the cost.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Client’s Budget</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The client budget and features play a vital role in developing or designing the WordPress website.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Skill and Experience</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The overall experience of the developer also helps to determine the cost of WordPress.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Some popular stats of WordPress development</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">WordPress covers almost 34% of the website on the internet</span></li>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">In the CMS market, WordPress consists of 60.8% of the market share</span></li>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Using WordPress CMS, approx 14.7%  of the world’s top website</span></li>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">There are more than 60,000 plugins present in the WordPress Plugin Directory</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Above mentioned stats can be enough to choose WordPress over other web development projects. The main question arises now: the cost for the development of the website in 2020. </span></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1908 size-full" src="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screen_shot_2020_08__XA6Uz.jpg" alt="wordpress development" width="1024" height="457" srcset="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screen_shot_2020_08__XA6Uz.jpg 1024w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screen_shot_2020_08__XA6Uz-300x134.jpg 300w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screen_shot_2020_08__XA6Uz-768x343.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">How much WordPress website development cost?</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">WordPress can be easily downloaded, free to use and now one can use it according to the needs. This is free but it won’t be able to live on a website; one has to spend money on facts that will estimate the cost of <a href="https://www.aryausa.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WordPress Web Developmen</a>t such as hosting fees, domain name cost, premium theme, and plugins.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Hosting Cost</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Which web host to choose for investing is an important choice when developing a website. Web hosting can range from $3 to $200 per month. Hosting is reserving little space for your website. For hosting the website most recommended sites are Site Ground, Blue host, WPEngine etc. The website hosting cost very less as compared to others. </span></p>
<table style="height: 258px;" width="411">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="font-weight: 400; border: 1px dotted #080808; text-align: center;"><strong>Hosting Sites</strong></td>
