					<description><![CDATA[<p>Artificial Intelligence is changing the way we use technology. In a recent article found that 80% of the companies will be using chatbots by 2021.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/why-80-of-businesses-are-approaching-chatbots-in-2020">Why 80% of Businesses Are Approaching Chatbots In 2021?</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog">Aryavrat</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Artificial Intelligence is changing the way we use technology. A recent article found that 80% of the companies will be using chatbots by 2020.  Chatbots are interactive software that is used in apps, live chats, emails, and SMS, and behave like humans.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Many business owners said that they will use a chatbot in sales, marketing, and customer service. 42% of owners believe that in automation technology customer experience will improve and 48% said they are already using a chatbot for their business function.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Benefits of chatting with rather than using traditional channel</span></h2>
<ol>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">It is faster than any other means of communication</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Provides higher quality feedback</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Answers are honest</span></li>
</ol>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Chatbots provide a more personalized service experience for customers. A chatbot is a perfect tool to confidently transition leads from consideration to conversion. The main reason for investing is to improve the customer experience and another reason is that customers don’t like to wait in this fast-moving world. It is forecasted that the chatbot market will reach $1.25 billion by 2025.</span></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1936 size-full" src="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/workspace_with_robot_UohZX.jpg" alt="workspace-with-robot-working-computer-keyboard-top-view" width="626" height="313" srcset="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/workspace_with_robot_UohZX.jpg 626w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/workspace_with_robot_UohZX-300x150.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The on-time response is the key to meet customer expectations. No one in this fast-paced world wants to wait for hours before the support team turns up for the user queries. Whatever your service or product is, your business success depends on how strongly you are connected to your users, and how quickly you resolve your customer queries. Every chatbot provider is updated with the latest trend of AI and voice assistants to keep up with the technology enhancement and offer a constant brand experience.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">How Chatbot helps businesses to improve customer services and support</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Let’s discuss the Importance of adopting <a href="https://www.aryausa.com/Iot-solution" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Artificial Intelligence</a> in your business and how you can win new customers and retain the existing ones.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Customer Support Enhancement</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Human customer support agents can handle only a few concerns at a time but with the help of chatbots, organizations can handle an undefined number of customers. By this productivity of businesses can be boosted and allow human agents to focus on other tasks.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Satisfied Customer</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">By chatbot user-friendly conversation can be started by providing customers better satisfaction with a quick and relevant response. Bots with advanced technology can understand the query and answer the best possible solution.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Interaction Like Human</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Without any human effort, the chatbot can engage and respond to customers. Businesses with a chatbot can save time as customers don’t have to go for a frustrating process. </span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Lessen Efforts and costs</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">By using </span>AI and chatbot technology<span style="font-weight: 400;"> businesses can save more than 29% expense from the original cost. Bots help to lessen the service cost and speed up the response time without agent involvement. </span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">User Need Analyzing</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Bots can understand the user’s voice and analyze customer sentiments that help businesses from loss. One chatbot is enough to solve the queries of many users and avoid the case of customer dissatisfaction. </span></p>
<p><a href="https://www.aryausa.com/get-in-touch" target="_blank" rel="https://www.aryausa.com/get-in-touch noopener noreferrer"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1937 size-full" src="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/request_a_quote_15.jpg" alt="Request A Quote " width="750" height="170" srcset="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/request_a_quote_15.jpg 750w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/request_a_quote_15-300x68.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" /></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Wrap Up</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Implementing a chatbot is a smart choice for any business that wants to boost its productivity, engagement, and customer base. With the help of AI voice bots, brands can give a human touch to the conversation with the user and enhance business value. If you want to know the power of chatbot and make your business acknowledgeable in today’s world contact the </span><a href="https://www.aryausa.com/bot-development" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Best Chatbot Development Company</a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> today.</span></p>
