		<title>What Are The Top Web Services To Build Your Own Video Calling App?</title>
		<link>https://www.aryausa.com/blog/top-web-services-to-build-your-own-video-calling-app</link>
					<comments>https://www.aryausa.com/blog/top-web-services-to-build-your-own-video-calling-app#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 10 Jul 2020 12:33:16 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Mobile App Development]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Technology]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Web app Development Company]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Web Application Development]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.aryausa.com/blog/?p=1449</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>Nowadays with the improvement in the smartphone technologies video calling apps have become hugely popular over the past few years.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/top-web-services-to-build-your-own-video-calling-app">What Are The Top Web Services To Build Your Own Video Calling App?</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog">Aryavrat</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Nowadays with the improvement in smartphone technologies video calling apps have become hugely popular over the past few years. There are various eccentric mobile applications present for both Android and iPhones and still many more keep on coming up. There are many popular apps such as Skype, WhatsApp, Google Duo, Hangouts which are used by millions of people as a daily communication channel. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">With this developing trend and growing demand for <strong><a href="https://www.aryausa.com/mobile-app-development" target="_blank" rel="noopener">video conferencing apps like zoom</a></strong>, it&#8217;s never too late to develop a new business plan around it.   </span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Here is the list of top web services used to develop a video calling app</span></h2>
<p><a href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/couple_with_smartpho_0fMHe.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1958" src="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/couple_with_smartpho_0fMHe.jpg" alt="couple-with-smartphones-talking-through-video-call" width="626" height="313" srcset="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/couple_with_smartpho_0fMHe.jpg 626w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/couple_with_smartpho_0fMHe-300x150.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px" /></a></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Agora</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Agora is one of the real-time communication service providers that provide APIs and SDKs of its services that can be utilized by the developers to develop voice and video call applications. This provider includes features such as easy to set up with thoroughly documented APIs, low data latency as low as 0.2 seconds, help for up to 17 users in a video call, support for cross-platform native mobile apps as well as websites.</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Twilio</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Twilio has cloud sharing which provides API arrangements for complete users&#8217; journeys. This includes features such as availability of one-to-one as well as group calling, can record the call, share screens, low latency media routing, support from web browsers through an extension to support cross-platform calls.</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">QuickBlox</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Quickblox uses Extensible Messaging and Presence Protocol (XMPP) based chat connections and presents its services that are metered by the usage of the community. This is now a highly professional web service. This provides access to core files, can be fully customized according to project needs, there are useful code samples for different technologies that can cut down your project initialization cost.</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Sinch</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This is one of the most affordable video calling SDK solutions available in the market. This even provides 2500 free calling minutes to its users. They are feature-rich but provide simplistic SDKs for IOS, Android, and web applications that are easy to set up. They provide highly effective flash voice verification service and automatic call routing based on low latency.</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Tokbox</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Tokbox provides a number of features to be unique from its competitors. This service provides features like one-to-one video calls, group video calls, screen sharing, call recording, have low latency, support inter-device communication, highly secured with HIPAA, and BAA compliance. </span></p>
<p><a href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/request_a_quote_20.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1959" src="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/request_a_quote_20.jpg" alt="Request A Quote (20)" width="750" height="170" srcset="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/request_a_quote_20.jpg 750w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/request_a_quote_20-300x68.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" /></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The features provided by the organization are almost the same but the main key difference for selecting web services depends upon your usage, quality of services provided by the applications, and your business model. After selecting the web services you have to select the best and skilled </span><a href="https://www.aryausa.com/custom-software-development" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><b>Web Application Development Company in the USA</b></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> organization for app development.</span></p>
