					<description><![CDATA[<p>The impact of the coronavirus pandemic is growing rapidly and this affects every person in the world, it doesn't matter where they are living.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/how-technology-is-changing-due-to-coronavirus">How Technology Is Changing Due To Coronavirus?</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog">Aryavrat</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The impact of the coronavirus pandemic is growing rapidly and this affects every person in the world, it doesn&#8217;t matter where they are living and what they are doing.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Along with the individuals, this also affects businesses badly, that cause of the economic crisis all over the world.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In this pandemic situation; technology turned out to be our savior. From <a href="https://desktrack.timentask.com/blog/build-a-successful-remote-team/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Remote Work</a> to virtual events and for disease monitoring, technology played an important role. Technology nowadays is in the center stage and growing rapidly with new advancements and improvements. </span></p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Here are some conclusions of innovations in technology and industry because of COVID-19</span></h2>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Socialization and Mobile Communication due to Virtual Reality</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We are going through the biggest remote work practice in the business’s past. </span>Tools like slack, zoom, and Dropbo<strong>x</strong><span style="font-weight: 400;"> help us to digitally communicate and cooperate. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Virtual reality presents a delightful option to video calls, and this helps individuals to think that they are in space together. There can be a continued modification in virtual reality programs and </span><a href="https://www.aryausa.com/mobile-app-development" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mobile App Development</a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> that can benefit from everything from socialization to health support.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Next-Generation Network and Ubiquitous 5G Network</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">High speed and stable internet will be required for the market increase as we head to remote work. For health treatments and for monitoring coronavirus spread, China adopts a 5G network. As we all know COVID-19 needs outrageous </span><a href="https://www.aryausa.com/custom-software-development" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Web App Development </a><span style="font-weight: 400;">of telemedicine, video conferencing, and virtual reality world and for that, we all also require an internet upgrade.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Trusted Tracking and Misinformation Management</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">During this pandemic; the internet has received some dangerous viral media. For betterment, Twitter even organized a badge system issuing a blue checkmark for verified sources regarding coronavirus.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Mipasa is a transparent data hub promising to diminish the transmission of malicious knowledge by using blockchain technology which verifies the authenticity of data. This is associated with the partnership of IBM, Oracle, and the World Health Organization.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Biosensors: To Track Health Information</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Corresponding to the present condition of this pandemic every resident requires a biometric bracelet that can supervise their body temperature and heart rate 24 hours a day. A healthcare company Medopad in this situation provides assistance to the health care department by giving doctors a remote patient monitoring platform. This will serve to supervise ill and at endanger patients, giving insights by prioritizing the resources and acknowledging them beneficially.        </span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Artificial Intelligence: Vaccines and Drug Development</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In these problems of communal health disasters, to protect the acceleration of pharmaceutical development; Artificial Intelligence can aid in overwhelming all the hurdles of vaccine development and even hurry things up. <a href="https://www.aryausa.com/bot-development" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Artificial Intelligence</a> screens the millions of chemical compounds for potential drugs in simulation analyses quicker than individuals could and classifies objectives that new pharmaceuticals can latch onto to slow the increase of infection.     </span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Future can be way Different</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">There will be no manuscript for our present condition. No one realizes for sure how the world will look like after the catastrophe has diminished. But we can expect to speed up the transformation of our present protocol and accessories. To know more &amp; upgrade with the technology connect: sales@aryausa.com</span></p>
