		<item>
		<title>How AI Enables Innovation in the Education Field?</title>
		<link>https://www.aryausa.com/blog/ai-enables-innovation-in-the-education-field</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2020 08:28:08 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[AI in Education]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Solutions]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Technology]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[AI Development Company]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[AI Development Company USA]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Artificial intelligence]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Artificial Intelligence Development Company]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Artificial Intelligence Development Company USA]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.aryausa.com/blog/?p=1162</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>Artificial intelligence seemed to be just a science-fiction subject: talking machines, that can think &#038; feel. However, scientists have recently made significant advances in this field.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/ai-enables-innovation-in-the-education-field">How AI Enables Innovation in the Education Field?</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog">Aryavrat</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">What is Artificial Intelligence?</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Artificial intelligence seemed to be just a science-fiction subject: talking machines, that can think &amp; feel. However, scientists have recently made significant advances in this field of computer science research.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Over the years, Artificial Intelligence, machine learning, and deep learning have received much attention. What difference does it make between these two terms, which is quite difficult to understand, and what is the connection between them?</span></p>
<h3>Machine Learning</h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">It is a branch of <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A.I._Artificial_Intelligence">Artificial Intelligence</a> science that aims to give machines the ability to “learn”. This is done by using algorithms that identify patterns based on received data; so machines can make decisions and make predictions, that is, become “smart”. In this way, it is no longer necessary for the machine to be programmed specifically for each individual action.</span></p>
<h3><b>Deep Learning</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">On the other hand, it is a branch of Machine Learning Science that represents the most <a href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/AI-Transformation-in-Software-Testing-1-2-1024x576-1.png">advanced field of artificial intelligence</a>. It has the main objective of giving machines the ability to learn and think as much as humans.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">The Impact of Artificial Intelligence in </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">the Education Sector</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The world is changing rapidly around us. As days will increase, it is getting more difficult to keep up with the innovations that could change things as we know it now. The introduction of AI is a step that is creating an empire in technology.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Introducing Al in the educational arena is going to have a profound effect on a continuous area. Now it&#8217;s the right time for educational centers to take advantage of technological advancements and modify their environments accordingly to reach new heights of a productivity booster.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">AI plays a big role in the education sector, AI in the education sector could help teachers to do their jobs better and more efficiently. It creates new adaptive learning techniques, AI has already been making an impact on education. As per the latest trend; there is a high enrollment rate of students for online courses which can be easily managed by using AI technology. AI can help to improve the learning experience. </span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Benefits of AI in the Education Sector </span></h2>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><b>Simplifying administration process:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">  AI manages the administrative processes &amp; tasks easily and manages massive amounts of data to accumulate for the education centers. AI helps to identify and predict risks, automate the services.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><b>Smart learning process:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> It will provide smart learning solutions for students, which includes smart learning classrooms, robotics, and smart virtual assistants for students and this is one of the major benefits of smart classroom technology. </span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><b>Capability to monitor students:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> AI will be able to monitor the students in the classrooms without waiting for the exam results to see the student&#8217;s performance. Teachers can get access to see how students are learning their lessons, monitor student&#8217;s activity &amp; progress. </span></li>
</ul>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Final Thoughts </span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/elearning-web-app-development">AI in Education,</a> empowering the education sector with automation and geniuses. AI is the most reliable part of this segment lies in the automation of almost all kinds of learning resources. These are helping both teachers and students to work efficiently with the desired needs of children. AI in education is changing the way of thinking and solutions.</span></p>
