					<description><![CDATA[<p>Are you looking for extraordinary ways to maximize sales and growth in your E-commerce business?<br />
The E-commerce industry has experienced robust growth over the past five years.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/7-e-commerce-strategies-to-boost-up-your-business">7 eCommerce Strategies to Grow your Business Online!</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog">Aryavrat</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="pl-1148" class="panel-layout">
<div id="pg-1148-0" class="panel-grid panel-no-style">
<div id="pgc-1148-0-0" class="panel-grid-cell" data-weight="1">
<div id="panel-1148-0-0-0" class="so-panel widget panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="0">
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Are you looking for extraordinary ways to maximize sales and growth in your E-commerce business?</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The E-commerce industry has experienced robust growth over the past five years. Revenue is expected to show an annual growth rate (CAGR 2020-2024) of 7.6%, resulting in a market volume of US $3,004,191m by 2024. User penetration is 56.1% in 2020 and is expected to hit 65.5% by 2024.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As the E-commerce industry is increasing day by day, it is becoming a most competitive market all over the world and if you are new to the market you need to find innovative strategies to keep the customers engaged, increase sales and build a reputation that will help you to increase your business revenue.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">A Harvard Business School study found that 75% of E-commerce startups failed. Launching an E-commerce business is not an easy task, the high failure rate can seem discouraging.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-2005 size-full" src="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/online_travel_sale_s_HQtqc.jpg" alt="E-commerce Services" width="1024" height="853" srcset="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/online_travel_sale_s_HQtqc.jpg 1024w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/online_travel_sale_s_HQtqc-300x250.jpg 300w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/online_travel_sale_s_HQtqc-768x640.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div id="pl-1148" class="panel-layout">
<div id="pg-1148-0" class="panel-grid panel-no-style">
