										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Are you a Travel agent finding extraordinary ways to improve sales and maximize your startup business growth?</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Nowadays, The travel industry is growing rapidly without any sign of slowing down. According to the WTTC, last year the travel industry grew 3.9 percent, above global GDP growth of 3.2 percent, and contributing a record $8.8 trillion to the world economy. The report also found that the travel and tourism industry generated 10.4 percent of all global economic activity last year.</span></p>
<h2><b>Technology Enhance </b><b>The Travel Industry</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Technology has played a vital role in creating your travel business&#8217;s online presence. The future of the travel industry will be technology-driven. It is one of the most important aspects of the travel industry in obtaining a competitive advantage. Technology has changed the way the customer book a trip.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As the travel industry is increasing day by day, it is becoming a most competitive market all over the world and if you are new to the market you need to find innovative strategies to keep the customers engaged, increase sales and build a reputation that will help you increase your business revenue.</span></p>
<h2>Ways To Improve Travel Business Online</h2>
