		<title>How We Can Revolutionize the Banking Industry with Chatbots?</title>
		<link>https://www.aryausa.com/blog/revolutionizing-the-banking-industry-with-chatbot</link>
					<comments>https://www.aryausa.com/blog/revolutionizing-the-banking-industry-with-chatbot#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2019 07:31:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Chatbot Development]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Chat-bot Development]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Chatbot Development Comapny]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Chatbot Development Company USA]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Chatbot Development Solution USA]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Chatbot Services]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Chatbot Services USA]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Chatbot Solutions]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.aryausa.com/blog/?p=997</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>A Chatbot that can help banks, increase these boundaries, navigate the users as per their needs, help them get clarity of products and services.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/revolutionizing-the-banking-industry-with-chatbot">How We Can Revolutionize the Banking Industry with Chatbots?</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog">Aryavrat</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In the last few years, the banking sector has been going through a rough patch. However, to get its operations back on track effective banking solutions are required which provide flawless accessibility and customer service. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The banking industry faces one major challenge and that is user experience. Banks struggle to engage with customers or provide them with a good digital experience. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">A Chatbot that can help banks, increase these boundaries, navigate the users as per their needs, help them get clarity of products and services. Thus, a chatbot becomes a clear need of time!</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Why we use Chatbot in Banking Automation?</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Millions of customers come with billions of queries to find solutions, but do you know that only 20% of their queries or problems related to finances are deeply unique, while the rest 80% of these are frequent and general inquiry and the </span>bot <span style="font-weight: 400;">can easily handle these frequent queries and unique problems simultaneously. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Since each conversation is a new business opportunity. Chatbot or virtual assistant will help banks create an attractive and interactive environment by providing uninterrupted service through the name.</span></p>
<h3><b>Characteristics of Chatbot </b></h3>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">ChatBot can help customers with basic to higher information such as account balance and other consultations immediately.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">ChatBot can help the customer service staff that deals with the frequently asked questions and help them improve the client&#8217;s centric approach from a broader perspective. </span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">ChatBots will encourage your customers by giving them the power of choosing appropriate things they&#8217;ll meet their requirements last but not least.</span></li>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">A ChatBot is customizable and driven by predictive analytics artificial intelligence and natural facts.</span></li>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">A ChatBot can act as your personal financial adviser with its access to all the data points to its ability to draw patterns with the transactional behavior and other banking processes that have undergone across each account. that can give clarity to the customers and help them make a better decision. </span></li>
</ul>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Which type of Services Chatbot provides in the Banking Industry</span><img loading="lazy" class="alignright wp-image-2044" src="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/chatbotinthemyth.jpg" alt="How Chatbot Can Boost Banking Aytomation" width="437" height="437" srcset="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/chatbotinthemyth.jpg 500w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/chatbotinthemyth-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/chatbotinthemyth-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.aryausa.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/chatbotinthemyth-200x200.jpg 200w" sizes="(max-width: 437px) 100vw, 437px" /></h2>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">My Account queries</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Update Account Info</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Service/Product Request</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">EMI Calculator</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Funds and Payees</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Alerts and Offers</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Customer Support</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Easy Credit Card Process</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Easy Loans Process </span></li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3>Use case of Bots in Banking</h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">A virtual assistant <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chatbot" target="_blank" rel="noopener">chatbot</a> can take commands via type and voice command and perform functions such as scheduling payment and exploring recent transactions within their app.</span></p>
<h3><b>The Integration of Chatbots helps Banks to:</b></h3>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Facilitate two-way communication by replacing channels such as phone, text, email, etc.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Offer quick transactional and customer support</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Provide employee assistance</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Measure customer satisfaction</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Guide on financial matters</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Streamline routine back-office tasks</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Offer personalized marketing strategy</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To serve their tech-savvy consumers more banks are leveraging <strong>AI <a href="https://www.aryausa.com/bot-development">Chatbot Solutions</a></strong>. Thus, improve their digital banking experience.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">According to the study, by 2021, chatbots will be handling around 85% of the customer service interactions without any human support that saves billions of dollars. </span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Chatbots can improve Customer Experience in Banking in many ways:</span></h2>
<ol>
<li><b> Personalized Banking Experience: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Chatbots can effectively provide account statements. Chatbots can also help provide information related to the latest banking schemes, KYC, and resolve queries quickly.</span></span></li>
<li><b> Ease of use:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Chatbot is a platform developed to understand, learn, and talk like a human being that provides conversation experiences similar to those of humans, and efficiency greatly contributes to improving the customer experience.</span></span></li>
<li><b> Automate Banking Process:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Chatbot can help the automotive industry in many ways, for the process, for the customers.</span></span></li>
<li><b> Simplified Workforce: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">In a robotic workforce that offers cost-effective and accurate process execution within seconds</span></span></li>
<li><b> Fraud Prevention:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Chatbots identifies the context in the text and works over accurately replicating human intelligence, preventing and detecting fraud.</span></span></li>
<li><b> 24*7 support:</b> <span style="font-weight: 400;">Access bank records policy documents or certificates at any time anywhere.</span></li>
</ol>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Time is valuable. For that reason, Bot is the foremost demanding feature, therefore, every industry requires, and especially in the banking sector, it has various advantages. These Chatbots can play a crucial role in assisting humans to handle customer queries</span></p>
