		<title>12  Reasons Android Are Steps Ahead than iPhone</title>
		<link>https://www.aryausa.com/blog/12-reasons-to-ditch-the-apple-iphone-for-android</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 24 Nov 2015 10:06:51 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Solutions]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.aryausa.com/blog/?p=287</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>The first and most obvious difference between iPhone and Android is the plethora of devices and its accessories available with Android.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/12-reasons-to-ditch-the-apple-iphone-for-android">12  Reasons Android Are Steps Ahead than iPhone</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog">Aryavrat</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>The first and most obvious difference between iPhone and Android is the plethora of devices and its accessories available with Android. Due to this factor android devices are cheaper and more preferable than iPhone.. As a result there are far more Android phones out there to choose.</li>
<li>When you have an Android phone, your notifications are always displayed at the top of the screen. Notification drags user’s attention to check it.</li>
<li>Android does not force you to keep all your apps on Home screen as iPhone do.</li>
<li>You can customize your phone easily as compared to iPhone.</li>
<li>Android provides many ways to his users to lock his phone like pattern lock or face lock. But iPhone provide only passcode or fingerprint lock only.</li>
<li>Apple’s baked-in maps isn’t good as Google maps. But you can’t make Google maps your default.</li>
<li>You can set multiple accounts at same Android tablet.</li>
<li>Google’s app store allows you to download apps directly from its website. But when you search any iPhone app from browser, you will need to launch iTunes or App store to download the app.</li>
<li>With iPhone it is necessary to use Apple’s proprietary “Lightning“cable. But with Android you can use any micro USB.</li>
<li>Android doesn’t care where your music comes from. But you need iTunes if you want to load up your phone with songs and you need iPhotos if you want to get photos onto your computer.</li>
<li>Apple’s phone screen size is less as compared to Android. As iPhone 6Plus has 5.5 inch screen size but some people want large screen with easier to use keyboardand more immersive browsing and movie watching experience.</li>
<li>The battery in an iPhone is fixed with no option to swap it out. But with android you can remove the battery and replace it with new one.</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/12-reasons-to-ditch-the-apple-iphone-for-android">12  Reasons Android Are Steps Ahead than iPhone</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog">Aryavrat</a>.</p>
