		<title>7 Breakthroughs iOS 9 Has Made For iPhones</title>
		<link>https://www.aryausa.com/blog/7-breakthroughs-ios-9-has-made-for-iphones</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 20 Nov 2015 11:15:21 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Solutions]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.aryausa.com/blog/?p=262</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>Apple added many new features to the maps too. Now you can use public transport with Maps as your guide.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/7-breakthroughs-ios-9-has-made-for-iphones">7 Breakthroughs iOS 9 Has Made For iPhones</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog">Aryavrat</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="p17"> iOS 9 brings key enhancements to the powerful built-in apps on iPhone and iPad that is designed for the essential things you use every day — like mail, messages, web browsing, maps, making notes, and so much more.</p>
<p class="p17"><strong>iOS 9 Highlights</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Improved Battery life and Performance</strong> &#8211; Apple states that iOS 9 gives additional battery life hours and there is a new low power mode in the device which increase up to three additional hours of usage.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>Upgraded Apple Maps</strong> &#8211; Apple added many new features to the maps too. Now you can use public transport with Maps as your guide. In selected cities around the world, a new Transport view shows you stations and routes for the metro, buses, trains and ferries on the map. So it makes your journey easy whenever you plan.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>Improved multitasking</strong> &#8211; iOS provides side-by-side app support and picture-in-picture video support which allows user to watch videos or shows they don’t want to miss while they are working, it simply pops up the video to the corner of the screen.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>Smarter Siri</strong>&#8211; &#8211; You know Siri as a helpful assistant you can have, but Siri is also the technology that powers your search on your iPhone and iPad. And it enhance your search results when you type anything in a search field.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>Addition of ‘News’ – </strong>Apple provides its users the new news apps like Flipboard and Zite. These apps helps you to keep updated with everything happening around.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>Addition of ‘QuickType</strong> &#8211; (iPads only) Place two fingers and slide over the screen so you will be able to use it like a touchpad by moving the cursor randomly. There is a shortcut bar on the iPad which helps the user to switch faster between apps.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>Security And Privacy</strong> -To keep your devices and Apple ID secure, it is essential to protecting your personal information — like photos, documents, messages, email and so much more. OS 9 provides advance security to its users by strengthening the passcode. It protect your phone from unauthorized access. These new security features are easy to use and make it harder to for someone else to access your personal information.</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
