		<item>
		<title>Mx Player &#8211; Play Everything</title>
		<link>https://www.aryausa.com/blog/mx-player-play-everything</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 09 Nov 2015 05:18:12 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[APP BULLETIN]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.aryausa.com/blog/?p=237</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>MX Player is the first Android video player which supports multi-core decoding. Test result proved that dual-core device’s performance is up to 70% better than single-core devices.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/mx-player-play-everything">Mx Player &#8211; Play Everything</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog">Aryavrat</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>MX Player &#8211; The best way to enjoy your movies.<br />
a) HARDWARE ACCELERATION &#8211; Hardware acceleration can be applied to more videos with the help of new HW+ decoder.</p>
<p>b) MULTI-CORE DECODING &#8211; MX Player is the first Android video player which supports multi-core decoding. Test result proved that dual-core device’s performance is up to 70% better than single-core devices.</p>
<p>c) PINCH TO ZOOM, ZOOM AND PAN &#8211; Easily zoom in and out by pinching and swiping across the screen. Zoom and Pan is also available by option.</p>
<p>d) SUBTITLE GESTURES &#8211; Scroll forward/backward to move to next/previous text, Up/down to move text up and down, Zoom in/out to change text size.</p>
<p>e) KIDS LOCK &#8211; Keep your kids entertained without having to worry that they can make calls or touch other apps. (plugin required)</p>
