					<description><![CDATA[<p>Link2SD is an application manager that makes it easy for Android device to move applications to the SD card. It enables you to manage your apps and storage easily</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog/link2sd">Link2SD</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aryausa.com/blog">Aryavrat</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Link2SD is an application manager that makes it easy for Android device to move applications to the SD card. It enables you to manage your apps and storage easily.</p>
<p><b>Features:</b><br />
<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.0.1/72x72/2714.png" alt="✔" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Link apk, dex and lib files of apps to SD card<br />
<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.0.1/72x72/2714.png" alt="✔" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Link internal data of apps to SD card <b>(Plus)</b><br />
<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.0.1/72x72/2714.png" alt="✔" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Link dex files of the system apps to SD card <b>(Plus)</b><br />
